data.description: This hard-to-find, contemporary, ranch home HAS IT ALL! From the quiet street w/private, neighborhood trails to the impressive main floor (almost 1350 SF!) with 3 nice-sized BRs including a full BA plus a MBR w/en suite shower-bath MBA, a contemporary kitchen: white cabinets/stainless/granite, backsplash/under- & in-cabinet/drawer lighting! Multiple living/family areas on the main PLUS a BR w/walk-in closet, spa-bath w/shower + SAUNA & a great-room sized family room downstairs PLUS extra storage/unfinished space. An oversized GA w/brand-new OVERSIZE driveway includes parking along garage for RV/trailers/etc! Sited in one of Mendota Heights best neighborhoods with 3 golf courses, endless shopping, miles of trails of all types, nature preserves, the riverway and Pickerel Lake all within a short walk. Easy+quick access to St Paul's sports+entertainment venues/cultural events/restaurants/the airport. Even options for multi-generational living/in-law apt/two floors of single-level living!
